### Get Account Balance
POST http://inviting.test/api/whatsapp/balance
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "phone_number": "07038606396"
}

### Get Transaction History
POST http://inviting.test/api/whatsapp/transactions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "phone_number": "07038606396",
    "limit": 5
}

### Initiate a Transfer
POST http://inviting.test/api/whatsapp/transfer
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "source_phone_number": "07038606396",
    "destination_account_number": "1234567890",
    "amount": 100.50
}

### Initiate a Bill Payment
POST http://inviting.test/api/whatsapp/bill-payment
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "source_phone_number": "07038606396",
